<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>New Client Details</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      }
      .header {
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #2c3e50;
        text-align: center;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #3498db;
        padding-bottom: 15px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .content {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .details {
        margin: 20px 0;
        padding: 15px;
        background: #f4f8fb;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      .details p {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #2c3e50;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin: 8px 0;
      }
      .details p strong {
        color: #3498db;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #777;
        margin-top: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        padding-top: 15px;
        border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
      }
      .cv-link {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #3498db;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 8px 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-top: 10px;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .cv-link:hover {
        background: #2980b9;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">📄 New Client Details</div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>A new client has submitted a request through the website. Here are the details:</p>

        <div class="details">
          <p><strong>First Name:</strong> {{firstName}}</p>
          <p><strong>Last Name:</strong> {{lastName}}</p>
          <p><strong>Phone Number:</strong> {{phone}}</p>
          <p><strong>Email Address:</strong> {{email}}</p>
          <p><strong>Message:</strong> {{message}}</p>
          
          <!-- إضافة رابط تحميل CV فقط إذا كان موجودًا -->
          {{#if file}}
          <p><strong>CV:</strong> <a class="cv-link" href="{{file}}" download>Download CV</a></p>
          {{/if}}
        </div>

        <p>Please follow up with the client as soon as possible.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>We appreciate your leadership, Please find the client's details below for your review.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
